OL,6,FThe report said Dr Aarella, who
OL,7,Fqualified in 1999 in India, had
OL,8,Fpreviously been suspended for 10
OL,9,Fmonths after he behaved in "a sexually
OL,10,Fmotivated manner" towards three female
OL,11,Fcolleagues between 2013 and 2015.
OL,13,FHe was handed a five-year restraining
OL,14,Forder in relation to one of the
OL,15,Fdoctors in September 2020 at
OL,16,FNottingham Crown Court.
OL,18,FThe suspension was imposed following a
OL,19,Ftribunal hearing in September 2022 but
OL,20,Fdid not come into effect immediately.
